 />"},{"pid":"73a642978ebc74bbd9e06c6b123386957bab5eb2","tid":493832,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點解自殺要講墜軌<br />\n好似比人推落去或者唔小心跌落去咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為唔知係自己跳/俾人推/意外</blockquote><br />\n就算發現真相<br />\n新聞都只係會用墜軌講自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd1fa1cbd5f4141f2a8be5f6c650f3e7f9b7ad1","tid":493832,"uid":96855,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩搭車廣播話有人沙田站誤闖路軌.. 誤闖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？咁撚大條鐵路，唔好同我講佢唔知係唔可以行</blockquote><br />\n覺得你呢種人好撚弱智 成日淨係用普通日常經驗去判斷嘢 大把突發case可以令一個人誤闖路軌啦 我唔係話佢一定有特殊事發生咗 但你都唔洗一嚟就用呢種口吻 反映你思路幾單純直接"},{"pid":"d31351397a5d87161bf6dd595cf2427ca599f018","tid":493832,"uid":62192,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩搭車廣播話有人沙田站誤闖路軌.. 誤闖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？咁撚大條鐵路，唔好同我講佢唔知係唔可以行</blockquote><br />\n唔通同你講有人跳軌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為有人跳軌，列車服務受阻，不便之處，敬請原諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3059e6a25be8cceaef260e958df3c5620f5067e","tid":493832,"uid":47128,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"做新聞/ 廣播應該盡可能用啲客觀啲嘅詞語<br />\n講墜軌/ 誤闖係好合理<br />\n唔通未有證據就話人哋跳軌咩"},{"pid":"a33d047145d60dce5fa3ecbe4e27092fdfcb053b","tid":493832,"uid":81183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我說道，「爸爸，你走吧。」他往車外看了看，說，「我買幾個橘子去。你就在此地，不要走動。」我看那邊月台的柵